# themes/_shared/ — pack-agnostic Handlebars partials.
#
# Templates here load alongside every pack and become available
# as Handlebars partials globally.  They compose pack primitives
# via {{> primitive-X}}; the partial dispatch resolves to whichever
# pack is currently loaded, so the same shared file produces
# Mantine output under one pack and shadcn output under another.
#
# Pack templates with the same logical name override the shared
# default (place a same-named .hbs in the pack and add it to the
# pack's emits map).
#
# Convention: shared templates that compose primitives belong here;
# the design-system-specific primitives live in each pack
# (themes/<pack>/primitive-X.hbs).
